data.description: *Assumable 2.75% Va loan with special terms, please ask agent for details.Nestled within picturesque Rancho Vistoso, this home backs up to the rugged wash which means there is a neighbor on each side but not behind the home. There is direct access from the back gate to the trails that run throughout this community. The layout of this 4 bed/3 bath home offers endless possibilities for whatever your family needs. Spacious bedrooms with big closets, an open loft, a large family room with a fireplace, an office featuring special order glass doors, a kitchen with an abundance of storage, and a large laundry room make this home cozy and comfortable. Any of these spaces could be configured to make it a 5 or 6 bed home.
